title: Image Search with Zilliz Cloud and PyTorch
description: On this page, we are going to go over a simple image search example using Zilliz Cloud. The dataset we are searching through is the Impressionist-Classifier Dataset found on Kaggle. For this example, we have re-hosted the data in a public google drive.
